Item.LongDesc:
cktuning specifies specifies the value of the tuning constant c (scalar greater than 0 which controls the robustness/efficiency of the estimator) and the prefixed value k (sup of the change-of-variance sensitivity) and the values of parameters A, B and d:
cktuning(1) = c;
cktuning(2) = k = supCVC(psi,x) x \in R;
cktuning(3)=A;
cktuning(4)=B;
cktuning(5)=d;
Remark: if length(cktuning)==2 values of A, B and d will be computed automatically
